&gt; I hope you&#39;ll give manual sweep a try. As I&#39;ve mentioned in other posts, I
have a number of the automated sweep devices, and the manual sweep results
can give any of them a run for their money. You can try just about any radio
that has a tight enough dial to rapidly move back and forth across the band.

