that all you have to do is hold down the tuner button (and keep holding) and
it sweeps automatically without being hacked. See if you can pick up a Sony
#SRF-M37V. I know other researchers who&#39;ve gotten good results with that.
Just add batteries and you&#39;re good to go. Oh, and an external speaker too. 
